Description: Smart Cloudflare DynDNS service
 cloudflare-register manages multiple hostnames across multiple Cloudflare
 zones with automatic IPv4/IPv6 detection, dual-stack record creation,
 update and cleanup, a JWT-protected web UI for adding hosts, a Textual
 TUI dashboard, and a `--sync --once` mode usable from cron.
